<br>
htt://www.geocities/garbink<br>
<br>
Expending the time to getting a normal exp group is VERY ineffiencent due to a number of reasons:<br>
<br>
1) You need certain classes...cleric, chanter, tank, etc.<br>
<br>
2) There is only one zone post 50 to get a pickup group...KC.<br>
<br>
3) People thinking they have a group..get together and have one of the key classes back up waisting a ton of time.<br>
<br>
4) Misc<br>
<br>
I spend ALOT of my time TRY to get a group when I could be getting exp!<br>
<br>
The recent posts about HS exp group and Effy group are great. I pray these groups get together cause I am up fer both of them.<br>
<br>
Sissy also posted on this subject on the general board...from all these places I got the idea.<br>
<br>
I think we should start forming &quot;Perstant Groups&quot;. What do I mean by that?<br>
<br>
I mean having a group of people get together at about the same time everyday and grouing together at least most of the week.<br>
<br>
For example: 7pm central Seb group. The six people in the group will meet on Mon Tue Thur at the orb. If something comes up he/she can email the group (or at least try to) so that a replacement can be made hopefully BEFORE I have to get in game and wait two hours.<br>
<br>
I am not limiting this to ONE group. We all work differnat hours and have differant scheduals. I think if we listed play times (both start and finish) and days here we can come up with some kick ass &quot;Persistant groups.&quot; Also please list the keys you have...HS Seb and class/lvl.<br>
<br>
I am trying to start a &quot;Persistant group&quot; for myself that starts around 8m Central.<br>
<br>
If you are interested please post below. Also, even if you are not interested in my 8m group...post your info here so maybe we can find a &quot;persistant group&quot; for you.<br>
<br>
Delane Spellsong 55 Bard CT<br>
